OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774012289
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Army
OL,4,Cofficer killed while training in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FThe death of a British Army officer
OL,8,Fkilled in a live firing training
OL,9,Fexercise in Northumberland is being
OL,10,Finvestigated by police and health and
OL,11,Fsafety inspectors, an inquest opening
OL,12,Fhas heard.
OL,14,FCaptain Philip Gilbert Muldowney, 25,
OL,15,Fdied on January 25 at Otterburn
OL,16,FTraining Area in Northumberland, one
OL,17,Fof the UK's largest army training
OL,18,Franges.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774012289
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Army
OL,4,Cofficer killed while training in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FOpening an inquest into his death at
OL,8,FNorthumberland Coroner's Court on
OL,9,FThursday, senior coroner Andrew
OL,10,FHetherington said Capt Muldowney,
OL,11,Fknown as Gilbert, was undertaking a
OL,12,Ftraining exercise at the range in
OL,13,FOtterburn Camp.
OL,15,F"An incident occurred which resulted
OL,16,Fin Gilbert suffering a gunshot wound,
OL,17,Fwhich is believed to have entered
OL,18,Fthrough his back and exited through
OL,19,Fhis left shoulder," Mr Hetherington
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774012289
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Army
OL,4,Cofficer killed while training in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FThe coroner said CPR was conducted by
OL,8,Fmilitary medics and ambulance crews
OL,9,Fattended, but Capt Muldowney was
OL,10,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,12,FMr Hetherington said the incident was
OL,13,Fbeing investigated by Northumbria
OL,14,FPolice, the Health and Safety
OL,15,FExecutive and the Defence Safety
OL,16,FAuthority, who are conducting a
OL,17,Fservice inquiry.
OL,19,FHe told the hearing: "In the
OL,20,Fcircumstances I formally open this
OL,21,Finquest and adjourn to May 19 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774012289
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Army
OL,4,Cofficer killed while training in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,F"However, this is very much a
OL,8,Fprovisional date and we will look at
OL,9,Fan alternative listing."
OL,11,FCapt Muldowney's parents attended the
OL,12,Fhearing on a videolink.
OL,14,FThe officer grew up in Ballinameen,
OL,15,Fnear Boyle, County Roscommon, in
OL,16,FIreland, after his family moved there
OL,17,Fwhen he was a child. He served as a
OL,18,Ffire support commander within 129
OL,19,F(Dragon) Battery of the 4th Regiment
OL,20,FRoyal Artillery, based in Thirsk in
OL,21,FNorth Yorkshire.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774012289
OL,3,CInquest opens into death of Army
OL,4,Cofficer killed while training in
OL,5,CNorthumberland
OL,7,FAfter his death, the Ministry of
OL,8,FDefence said Capt Muldowney was an
OL,9,F"immensely enthusiastic officer who
OL,10,Fembraced life with a vigour that
OL,11,Finspired those around him".
OL,13,FCapt Muldowney joined the army on
OL,14,FJanuary 5 2020, commissioning into the
OL,15,FRoyal Artillery on December 11 2020
OL,16,Fafter attending the Royal Military
OL,17,FAcademy Sandhurst.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
